snippet.title: IndestructoTank! GB (GamePlay Walkthrough)
snippet.description:
Use your enemy's own weapons against them and turn yourself into a DEADLY PROJECTILE!
You're indestructible... But remember to gather enough XP before your fuel runs out!
Then purchase even more enemies to smash the higher the combo,the more XP you gain!
